         'в€†WI SIZE ERROR: Cannot set "size" when "scale" is proportional; Use "extent" or "where" instead'##.Error 0=вЉѓscale
         'в€†WI DOMAIN ERROR: size'##.Errorв€Ё/0>arg
         sizeв†ђarg
     :EndSection
     :Section вЌќ Recompute APL+Win 'extent'
         marginsв†ђ+/2 2вЌґ+вЊїBorders[1;,2;] вЌќ Differences between 'extent' and 'size' (in pixels)
